div.p: Exception 8 with Error Code → Print All Registers → Halt
Error Code Format Always 0 for Double Fault Indicates exception occurred while handling another exception

ul.li: CPU reset is the only option

div.p: Print All Registers EIP, CS, EFLAGS EAX, EBX, ECX, EDX ESI, EDI, EBP, ESP DS, ES, FS, GS Error Code
Print Diagnostic Info "This usually indicates:" "- Kernel stack corruption" "- Exception in exception handler"
Prevents Triple Fault CPU would reset on unhandled exception
